# The CI edge-bump classifier (.github/workflows/ci.yml, job "changes") treats a
# subset of these excludes — docs/, test/, .github/, root-level *.md — as "does
# not ship". If you change what's excluded from the image here, update that
# classifier too, or a merge that now ships could skip its staging edge roll.
.git
.gitignore
.github
.env*
.nimblebrain
.DS_Store
**/node_modules
web/
test/
docs/
*.md
!package.json
